[Student "S"]
{WEST knows EAST has at least five \Ss, and they might provide discards for two or three 
of her minor suit losers.

She tries Blackwood and, sure enough, EAST comes through with two Aces.

Even with all the Aces WEST knows there are not enough points for Grand, 
so she bids 6\H.}

